<a href="/wiki/Obstructive_lung_disease" title="Obstructive lung disease">obstructive</a></div>
</td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-even">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><i>acute:</i> <a href="/wiki/Acute_bronchitis" title="Acute bronchitis">Acute bronchitis</a>
<p><i>chronic:</i> <a href="/wiki/Chronic_obstructive_pulmonary_disease" title="Chronic obstructive pulmonary disease">COPD</a> (<a href="/wiki/Chronic_bronchitis" title="Chronic bronchitis">Chronic bronchitis</a>, <a href="/wiki/Emphysema" title="Emphysema">Emphysema</a>, <a href="/wiki/Diffuse_panbronchiolitis" title="Diffuse panbronchiolitis">Diffuse panbronchiolitis</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Asthma" title="Asthma">Asthma</a> (<a href="/wiki/Status_asthmaticus" title="Status asthmaticus">Status asthmaticus</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Bronchiectasis" title="Bronchiectasis">Bronchiectasis</a></p>
<i>unspecified:</i> <a href="/wiki/Bronchitis" title="Bronchitis">Bronchitis</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Bronchiolitis" title="Bronchiolitis">Bronchiolitis</a> (<a href="/wiki/Bronchiolitis_obliterans" title="Bronchiolitis obliterans">Bronchiolitis obliterans</a>)</div>
</td>
</tr>
